---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Resize-It"
  description="Learn how Resize-It protects your privacy. We process all images locally in your browser without uploading to our servers."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="bg-white text-center font-crimson mt-[80px] md:mt-10">
    <h1 class="text-[40px] md:text-[50px] leading-tight">  
      Privacy
      <span class="text-primary">Policy</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg md:text-xl mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      Your privacy is our priority. Learn how we protect your data.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Last Updated -->
  <div class="mt-12 px-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
      Last Updated: November 22, 2025
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6 md:py-8 space-y-8">
    
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        At Resize-It, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your data. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our services.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-primary/20">
        <p class="font-crimson text-lg font-medium text-primary mb-2">Our Core Privacy Principle:</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          All image processing happens entirely in your browser. Your images never leave your device, and we never have access to them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Information We Don't Collect -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Information We Don't Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Because our tools process everything locally in your browser, we do NOT collect:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Your images or any visual content you process</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">File names or metadata from your images</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Settings or modifications you apply to images</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Personal information unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., contact form)</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Information We May Collect -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Information We May Collect</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-crimson text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-gray-900">1. Analytics Data</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            We may use privacy-focused analytics to understand how visitors use our website. This may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 ml-6">
            <li class="text-gray-700">• Pages visited and features used</li>
            <li class="text-gray-700">• Browser type and operating system</li>
            <li class="text-gray-700">• General location (country/city level only)</li>
            <li class="text-gray-700">• Time spent on the site</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-3">
            We use this data solely to improve our services and never track individual users.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-crimson text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-gray-900">2. Contact Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            If you contact us through our contact form or email, we collect the information you provide (name, email, message) solely to respond to your inquiry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-crimson text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-gray-900">3. Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We may use essential cookies to remember your preferences (like theme settings). We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How We Protect Your Data -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">How We Protect Your Data</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-white text-lg">🔒</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-crimson text-lg font-medium mb-1 text-gray-900">Local Processing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">All image operations happen in your browser using JavaScript. Your images never travel over the internet.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-white text-lg">🛡️</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-crimson text-lg font-medium mb-1 text-gray-900">Secure Connection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">We use HTTPS encryption to protect data transmitted between your browser and our website.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-white text-lg">🚫</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-crimson text-lg font-medium mb-1 text-gray-900">No Data Retention</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">We don't store your images on our servers because they never reach our servers in the first place.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Third-Party Services -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may use the following third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-primary">•</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Analytics Services</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">To understand website usage and improve our services</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-primary">•</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Hosting Provider</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">To host and serve our website</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-4">
        These services may collect their own analytics data. Please review their respective privacy policies for more information.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Your Rights -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Know what data we collect and how we use it</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Request deletion of any personal information you've provided</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Opt-out of analytics tracking (through your browser settings)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Contact us with any privacy concerns</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Children's Privacy -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Our services are available to all ages. Since we don't collect personal information through normal use of our tools, there are no special considerations for children. However, we recommend parental supervision for users under 13.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Us -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tertiary to-green-50 border-2 border-secondary/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-6 text-gray-900">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-primary/20">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@resize-it.com" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-medium">privacy@resize-it.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
          Or visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-medium">Contact Page</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <div class="mt-16 px-5 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-crimson text-[30px] md:text-[40px] mb-4">
        Your Privacy is Protected
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">
        Start using our tools with confidence—your images stay on your device.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-tertiary hover:bg-primary text-primary hover:text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-3xl font-crimson font-semibold transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out">
        Start Using Tools
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
